Interface LoadProfileEstimator

All Known Implementing Classes:
ConstantLoadProfileEstimator, DynamicLoadProfileEstimator, NestableLoadProfileEstimator
public interface LoadProfileEstimator
Estimates the LoadProfile of some executable artifact that takes some input data quanta and produces them.
